overview: These cowboys live in a man's world - where their day is long, sweaty, and hot. When they have a moment of down time with their fellow studs, their sexual instincts take over and they satisfy each other in true cowboy fashion: boots in the air, ridin' hard and shooting far. Featuring a barn-side trio, the hairiest fuck scene of the year, a reverse cowboy masterpiece and more, Cowboys Part Two will have you saying yee-haw.
title: Cowboys: Part Two
